Class ValueKey.AccelerometerSet

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.samsung.android.service.health.tracking.data.ValueKey.AccelerometerSet
  • Enclosing class:
    ValueKey<T>

    public static class ValueKey.AccelerometerSet
extends Object
    This class is a data set for tracking HealthTrackerType.ACCELEROMETER_CONTINUOUS.
    It provides X, Y and Z axes with raw data. Accelerometer data doesn't include gravity.

    The X, Y, and Z axes are defined as follows:

    1.0.0
